Helen Nakimuli (amụrụ na 2 Julaị 1985) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na onye omeiwu Uganda, onye na-egwu volleyball, onye otu nke iri na otu nke Uganda maka Kalangala District. Ọ bụ onye otu National Unity Platform (NUP).
A mụrụ Nakimuli n'obodo Lukuba, Kyamuswa sub-county na Kalangala n'aka onye ụkọchukwu Ọtọdọks, Rev

Nna Christopher Walusimbi na Maria Nalwanga Walusimbi bụbu onye kansụl mpaghara Kalangala maka Kyamuswa na Bubeke. Nakimuli malitere agụmakwụkwọ ya na ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị Bukasa, Hormisdallen Primary School na Bweyogerere na Wakiso, Our Lady of Good Counsel na Gayaza maka ọkwa ya, St
Augustine secondary school na Wakiso maka ọkwa ya dị elu tupu ọ banye na Mahadum Makerere.
Ọrụ ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Nakimuli malitere na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị St
Augustine dị ka onye isi nwanyị. O meriri Aidah Nabayiga ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu maka mpaghara Kalangala

Nakimuli bụ onye na-egwu volleyball kemgbe afọ 1998. Ọ bụ onyeisi ndị otu volleyball ụmụ nwanyị gara egwuregwu ndị omeiwu nke East Africa na Arusha, Tanzania. Ọ bụ onye otu COBAP Volleyball Club. O nyere aka na windo nke Kalangala iji nweta ndị ọka iwu mgbe ndị ọzọ chọrọ iwere ihe onwunwe di ha nwụrụ anwụ. Nakimuli nyere enyemaka nke gụnyere nri, ncha na ihe ndị ọzọ nye ndị agadi nọ na mpaghara Kalangala. Nakimuli nyere ndị ụlọ ha gbara ọkụ enyemaka. Nakimuli rịọrọ minista steeti maka microfinance, Haruna Kyeyune Kasolo ka ọ tinye mpaghara agwaetiti Buvuma na Namayingo na ndepụta nke ego Emyooga

Popu Ọtọdọks na Onyeisi Ndị Bishọp nke Alexandria na Africa niile, Obi ụtọ Chineke ya Theodore nke Abụọ nyere Nakimuli ihe nrite ụka iji kwado ọrụ nlereanya ya na Chọọchị Ọtọdọk, Uganda na ihe a kpọrọ mmadụ.
